---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="A bit about ashmartin.">
  <main class="about-main">

    <section class="about-block">
      <div class="label">About</div>
      <div class="about-text prose">
        <p>
          I'm Ash Martin. I like building things.
          Over the years that has meant starting companies, designing products, writing software,
          working with hardware, and spending a lot of time figuring out how ideas turn into real objects.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm most interested in projects that sit between worlds. Physical and digital. Art and engineering.
          Serious and experimental. Some become businesses. Some stay as prototypes in the garage. Both are worth doing.
        </p>
        <p>
          This site is a collection of notes, projects, and thoughts in progress.
          No roadmap, no theme, just whatever I'm working on right now.
        </p>
        <p>
          Previously at <a href="https://www.stridehealth.com">Stride</a>. Currently working on
          <a href="/projects">Vanguartisan</a> and figuring out what's next.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="now-block">
      <div class="label">Now</div>
      <ul class="now-list">
        <li class="now-item">
          <span class="now-title">Building Vanguartisan</span>
          <span class="now-desc">Redesigning the reading experience with better typography controls.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="now-item">
          <span class="now-title">Writing more, publishing less</span>
          <span class="now-desc">Trying to develop a consistent practice before worrying about audience.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="now-item">
          <span class="now-title">Reading: <em>Ways of Seeing</em></span>
          <span class="now-desc">John Berger. Late to it, but it's landing hard.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-block">
      <div class="label">Say hello</div>
      <div>
        <div class="contact-links">
          <a href="mailto:iamashmartin@gmail.com" class="contact-link">
            <span class="contact-icon">email</span>
            iamashmartin@gmail.com
          </a>
          <a href="https://x.com/iamashm" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="contact-icon">twitter</span>
            @iamashm
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/iamashm" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="contact-icon">github</span>
            iamashm
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="contact-note">
          I'm slow to reply but I do reply. If it's about a project collaboration
          or something you're building, I'm especially interested.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-main {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px 100px;
  }

  /* ── Shared block layout */
  .about-block,
  .now-block,
  .contact-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    align-items: start;
    gap: 0 64px;
    padding: 72px 0 64px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-block .label,
  .now-block .label,
  .contact-block .label {
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  /* ── About */
  .about-text { max-width: 64ch; }

  .about-text p { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .about-text p + p { margin-top: 20px; }

  /* ── Now */
  .now-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .now-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .now-title {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .now-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── Contact */
  .contact-block { border-bottom: none; }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .contact-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--fg);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    width: fit-content;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .contact-link:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  .contact-icon {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    min-width: 52px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .contact-link:hover .contact-icon { color: var(--accent); }

  .contact-note {
    margin-top: 32px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 48ch;
  }

  /* ── Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-main { padding: 0 20px 80px; }

    .about-block,
    .now-block,
    .contact-block {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      padding-top: 48px;
      padding-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .about-text p { font-size: 16px; }
  }
</style>
